socho Multiplication Table Generator
saaf

mano n = pucho("Kis number ka pahada chahiye? ")
# Convert input string to integer
mano num = int(n)

dikhao("Pahada of", num, "hai:")

socho Loop starts from 1 to 11 (to include 10)
phir i mein range_tak(1, 11):
    mano result = num guna i
    dikhao(num, "x", i, "=", result)